{"tid":2070560,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12月22日愛丁堡廣場 聲援維吾爾族人權集會 3名被告加控暴動罪","createTime":"2020-06-19T08:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T11:01:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c39fea7d66be8ae5c5cd34b2166521f0cc28106","tid":2070560,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F6219&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cy8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=491ba97b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/6219</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭 #提堂<br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官 #1222中環<br />\n👥D1陸(20)，D2梁(21)<br />\n#合併案件👤D3蕭(20) <br />\n<br />\n修訂控罪：<br />\n1) 意圖妨礙拘捕或檢控該人 (D1)<br />\n2) 襲擊警務人員(D2, D3)<br />\n<br />\n新增控罪：<br />\n3) 暴動 (D1, D2, D3)❗️<br />\n<br />\n被控於2019年12月22日，在中環愛丁堡廣場大會堂，試圖拉走被警員53734制服人士(即D3)，D2,D3則攻擊警員58747<br />\n<br />\n控方申請轉介案件至區域法院，並與同日案件合併。<br />\n<br />\n✅各被告准以原有條件保釋✅<br />\n案件押後至 2020年8月21日 14:30 於東區裁判法院再訊，等候轉介文件及文件夾，及轉介至區域法院。"},{"pid":"004ec7e8dc1c6068e6416f3f461e14381f445bfd","tid":2070560,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132f51ee188dc81ae3bfae7b8876973330b784aa","tid":2070560,"uid":231886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線，和平集會都控暴動？"},{"pid":"cbfa9097aef0a4664c8569372ae516118f464222","tid":2070560,"uid":21545,"like":